snippet.title: Luigi en Circusland gameplay (PC Game, 1994)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Luigi en Circusland, Dos PC game produced by Topo Soft in 1994 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/luigi-en-circusland/7857/
In Luigi en Circusland, you will guide Luigi as he explores different parts of a circus, while beating some of the evil clowns and other funny enemies.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
